# This is a PUBLIC template repo — it ships structure + docs only, never real coursework.
# Your actual papers, drafts, syllabi, and readings stay on your computer (and in YOUR
# own private backup repo), not published here.

# Your past papers (voice samples) — keep local
past-work/*
!past-work/README.md

# Finished drafts Claude produces — keep local
drafts/*
!drafts/README.md

# Per-class materials (syllabi, rubrics, prompts, readings, papers) — keep local,
# but keep each class folder's README (the placeholder syllabus + instructions)
current/*/*
!current/*/README.md

# Per-user local config (holds your personal Desktop path) — not for the public template
output-location.txt

# OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.tmp
~$*
